        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Lycocerus bifurcatus sp. nov. (A–C), L. nigrigenus sp. nov. (D–F, H) and L. kuatunensis (Wittmer, 1995) (G). (A, D) Aedeagus in ventral view; (B, E) aedeagus in dorsal view; (Bi) apex of laterophysis in lateral view; (C, F) aedeagus in lateral view; (G, H) female abdominal sternites VIII in ventral view. Note: Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
